title: The title of hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options", but it changes with settings.
OB: When accessing the hyperlink builder, the title is displaying incorrectly.
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should always be "Hyperlink Options" regardless of the settings.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Set a label hyperlink as "www.actuate.com".
2. Access the hyperlink builder and observe the title.
